 sequenceDiagram
     participant U as Browser / Client
     participant C as Controller
     participant S as Service Layer
     participant R as Repository Layer
     participant DB as Database
    participant V as View / Template

     U->>+C: HTTP Request (e.g., GET /products/1)
    Note over C: Validate Request

     C->>+S: getProductDetails(id)
     Note over S: Process Business Logic

     S->>+R: findById(id)
     R->>+DB: SELECT * FROM products WHERE id = ?
     DB-->>-R: Result Set / Records

    R-->>-S: Product Entity
     S-->>-C: Product DTO / Model

     C->>+V: addAttribute("product", data)
    Note over V: Render HTML Template
     V-->>-C: Final HTML Content

     C-->>-U: HTTP Response (200 OK)
